summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending Plat 226E, page 16, of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle (Ordinance 86300), to rezone certain property in the S.E. 1/4 of Section 29, Township 26 North, Range 4 East, W.M. from RM 800 to BN, contingent upon the recording of a properly executed, delivered and accepted property use and development. (Petition of Randolph A. Carter, C.F. 282904)
